Class DietChartController

  • java.lang.Object
    • thebabycareproject.DietChartController
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    javafx.fxml.Initializable

    public class DietChartController
extends java.lang.Object
implements javafx.fxml.Initializable
    Controller of the sub-section ' Diet Chart ' of section 'Nutriment' of the ' Food & Nutrition ' category. Loads weekly diet plan according to child's age and weight status. Loads icons according to child's age. Diet plan are saved as png images, created in PowerPoint.
